size not to pay its dividend,

00:30:22.525 --> 00:30:24.650
it's the equivalent of the
company almost going out

00:30:24.650 --> 00:30:25.040
of business.

00:30:25.040 --> 00:30:26.748
She also said it will
go out of business.

00:30:26.748 --> 00:30:31.340
I mean, her report hit
Wall Street like a blast

00:30:31.340 --> 00:30:34.390
