I think she was the cover
of "Fortune Magazine."

00:31:23.820 --> 00:31:25.361
She was considered
one of the great--

00:31:25.361 --> 00:31:27.990
and she is one of the great
financial minds of the era.

00:31:27.990 --> 00:31:30.250
But she paid a very
heavy price for it.

00:31:30.250 --> 00:31:33.270
And if it's not sexism,
