00:35:22.437 --> 00:35:24.770
They need to say, here is
specifically what's happening,

00:35:24.770 --> 00:35:26.270
specifically when
it will happen,

00:35:26.270 --> 00:35:28.580
and here's how I can
tell you it will happen.

00:35:28.580 --> 00:35:32.620
Now, intelligence analysts
need to adapt a new methodology

00:35:32.620 --> 00:35:36.560
where they continually warn
the decision maker about what's

00:35:36.560 --> 00:35:38.690
going to occur and
show them the things

00:35:38.690 --> 00:35:41.750
that will happen going forward
to prove they're correct.

00:35:41.750 --> 00:35:45.240
A great expression is, here's
what will happen next week,

00:35:45.240 --> 00:35:47.410
next month, next
year to show you

00:35:47.410 --> 00:35:49.440
that my scenario is correct.

00:35:49.440 --> 00:35:50.974
Another expression
to use is, here's

00:35:50.974 --> 00:35:52.640
what could happen to
show you I'm wrong.

00:35:52.640 --> 00:35:54.230
If we see this, I'm wrong.

00:35:54.230 --> 00:35:55.970
And the final tool,
